"><strong>Stakeholder</strong>A person or group affected by the problem, the process, or the eventual solution.</div><div class=\"term-card\"><strong>Engineering process</strong>A repeatable decision structure for turning an uncertain need into a justified, communicated solution.</div></div>\n</section>\n<section><h2>Practical Takeaways</h2>\n<ul><li>Start reports by stating the problem and success measures, not by describing the first solution that came to mind.</li><li>For every recommendation, be able to point to the constraint or criterion that made it reasonable.</li><li>Treat exam hurdles, submission rules, and assignment requirements as design constraints on your own study system.</li></ul>\n</section>\n"
